OL,5,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FBarnsley's A&E department is put
OL,7,     Funder the microscope. Advanced
OL,8,     FNurse Practitioner Dave tries to
OL,9,     Fget to the bottom of a patient's
OL,10,     Fpuzzling symptom - her tongue has
OL,11,     Fturned black!
OL,12,G0250 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Toby is spellbound by his
OL,14,     Fpatient, Gideon, Preston's
OL,15,     Fpart-time witch, and Dr Natalia
OL,16,     FSpierings tries to help a young
OL,17,     Fwoman with a scalp condition
OL,18,     Fusually found in middle-aged men.
OL,19,G0335 Home and Away
OL,20,     FSonny tells a lie. Harper goes out
OL,21,     Fon a date. Cash and Eden are
OL,22,     Ffractured.
